      "writtenOn": "2020-07-22T19:14:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I only define unresolved blocks here; later I extend them to grapheme cluster edges so the \"_T\" in TNR will not be broken. Also, now I could as unresolved only whitespaces inside the unresolved blocks and to have this situation \"_T\" must be resolved.",
